These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
City: miami, san-francisco
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, dubstep
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, cabbage
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, prince
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, february
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the owner of the frog is the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| City      | san-francisco     | miami       |
| Music-Genre         | folk   | dubstep     |
| Food           | pomegranate | cabbage   |
| Cigar   | prince   | chaman  |
| Birthday   | february | october |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Transport     | subway    | airplane   |

