.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: billiard, snooker
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, december
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, azure
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, documentary
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, corn
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the person eating corn##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
5. the person playing billiard is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | billiard    | snooker |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Birthday           | may | december  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Color   | orange     | azure   |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie         | documentary    |
| Food     | lettuce           | corn      |

